From John Neuharth Subject Re New Uniforms writes While I enjoy the trend towards the more classic style of uniform and I disagree with the person who wants a return to the non gray road uniforms it should be remembered that one of the if not THE reason for the redesigning of uniforms especially hats re the new road all green A's caps and the cardinal navy blue road cap is the marketing money to be made in sales of new no ask the White too bad John Neuharth